title: -XBT- Business Plan Pro 11.0 Premier Edition 2009
description:
This is Business Plan Pro v11 from Palo Alto software.

CONFIRED FULLY WORKING!


INSTRUCTIONS:

1) DISCONNECT FROM INTERNET (!IMPORTANT!)

2) Install by double clicking file: "Business Plan Pro 11.0.exe"

3) At serial screen, use serial: BPPRU S11YF JF2R7 2473R

4) Finish install. DO NOT LAUNCH PROGRAM! Box should be UNCHECKED!

5) Run the application "Business Plan Pro 11.0" from the desktop shortcut

6) It asks if you want critical updates. NO!! Choose "LATER" and check "NEVER ASK ME AGAIN". (!!IMPORTANT!!)

7) UNCHECK "Automatic Updates" on the next popup. (!!IMPORTANT!!)

6) UNCHECK "Customer Driven Improvement Program" on the next popup. (!!IMPORTANT!!)

7) Click OK.

8) On next popup, (STILL DISCONNECTED FROM INTERNET!), choose "Call Us To Activate"

9) Now the next popup is Telephone Activation page ("Activation Wizard"). READ CLOSELY TO THE NEXT INSTRUCTIONS!

a) Open the keygen which is for "Marketing Plan Pro" - that doesn't matter. You still use this keygen.

b) In the keygen, Replace "SerialNo:" field with this: BPPRUS11YFJF2R72473R
WARNING! NO SPACES IN THE "SerialNo:" FIELD!! (!!IMPORTANT!!)

c) IGNORE the GenSerID button in the keygen. DON'T TOUCH IT!

d) On the Telephone Activation page, get the Activation ID (it will be all numbers) and enter it into the field "ActivationID:" in the keygen.

e) Now click the GetConfID button in the keygen. Enter this into the Telephone Activation page where it says "Enter the Confirmation ID".

f) Click "Next". If you see "Activation Complete", then you are successful. If not, then RE-READ THE ABOVE INSTRUCTIONS AND TRY AGAIN!!

10) On the next screen, it says to Register Software. Click "NO I DON'T WANT TO REGISTER". (!!IMPORTANT!!)

11) Click Finish button.

SUCCESS!


NOTE: THE KEYGEN IS FOR MARKETING PLAN PRO BUT IT DOESN'T MATTER, YOU STILL USE THIS! READ THE INSTRUCTIONS!!!
